title: PiratesOfPenzanceAVI-1983
description:
The Pirates of Penzance (1983) ( http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0086112/ )

VHS out of print for years, never released on DVD.  This is a fair-to-middling quality VHS-AVI transfer with good audio.  There is a bit of tracking noise on the bottom of the picture throughout and about a minute of tracking noise covering the whole screen around halfway through.  However, it is the only copy I have ever found on BitTorrent, and it made my wife very happy.

English, no subtitles.
